13. Write a Java program using substring() , indexof(), + , for replacing “was” to “is”
“Thwas was a test. Thwas was, too.”
public class ReplaceSubstringDemo {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String originalString = "Thwas was a test. Thwas was, too.";

        // Using substring(), indexOf(), and +
        String replacedString = originalString.substring(0, originalString.indexOf("was"))
                + "is" + originalString.substring(originalString.indexOf("was") + 3);

        System.out.println("Replaced String: " + replacedString);
    }
}
